dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes decorative cartouche will ill. of local peoples. Dedicated to Theodorus Tholing. Printer's mark "I 9". From Blaeu's "Theatre du Monde ou nouvel atlas". 1 map: col.; 37 x 49 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
